<p style="margin-top:15px;">Located off Highway 102 and within minutes of Downtown, Halifax Shopping Centre is easily accessed from all directions. Using Metro Transit? Over 150 buses make stops at the center each day.</p>
<p><strong>Address:</strong> 7001 Mumford Road, Halifax, N.S.</p>
<p><strong>Customer Service:</strong> (902) 453-1752</p>
<h5>From Quinpool Road</h5>
<p>Proceed West on Quinpool and turn right onto Connaught Avenue, proceed North on Connaught Avenue to Bayers Road, turn left onto Bayers Road, turn left at the first light.</p>
<h5>From Citadel Hill, Downtown Halifax</h5>
<p>Follow Rainnie Drive or Bell Road to Quinpool Road, proceed West on Quinpool Road, turn right onto Connaught Avenue, proceed North on Connaught Avenue to Bayers Road, turn left onto Bayers Road, turn left at the first light.</p>
<h5>From Halifax International Airport</h5>
<p>Take Highway 102 Southbound toward Halifax, follow Highway 102 to Bayers Road inbound, turn right at second light.</p>
<h5>From South Shore</h5>
<p>Follow Highway 103 turning right on Exit 18 to Highway 102. Follow Highway 102 to Bayers Road inbound, turn right at the second light.</p>
<h5>From the Annapolis Valley</h5>
<p>Follow Highway 101 turning right on Exit 1G to Highway 102, take Highway 102 Southbound towards Halifax, follow Highway 102 to Bayers Road inbound, turn right at second light.</p>
</div>
